		<h2>List of contributions</h2>
		<ul>
<li><span class="info">(<a href="../atem2006s/index.html">ATEM 2006 SI</a>)</span> Served as an <a href="https://doi.org/10.1049/iet-sen:20089010">Editor</a></li>
<li><span class="info">(<a href="../sle2008/index.html">SLE 2008</a>)</span> Served as a <a href="https://www.sleconf.org/2008/Committees.html">General Chair</a></li>
<li><span class="info">(<a href="../sle2008s/index.html">SLE 2008 SI</a>)</span> Served as an <a href="https://www.proquest.com/openview/8e96891c23c1e60966bcbeef97505845/1?cbl=21418">Editor</a></li>
<li><span class="info">(<a href="../sle2009/index.html">SLE 2009</a>)</span> <em>Coauthored <a href="../sle2009/paper03.html">Study of an API Migration for Two XML APIs</a></em> (<a href="../profile/ThiagoTonelliBartolomei.html">Thiago Tonelli Bartolomei</a>, <a href="../profile/KrzysztofCzarnecki.html">Krzysztof Czarnecki</a>, <a href="../profile/RalfLämmel.html"><span class="info">Ralf Lämmel</span></a>, <a href="../profile/TijsvanderStorm.html">Tijs van der Storm</a>)</li>
<li><span class="info">(<a href="../sle2010/index.html">SLE 2010</a>)</span> <em>Coauthored <a href="../sle2010/paper08.html">Automated Co-evolution of GMF Editor Models</a></em> (<a href="../profile/DavideDiRuscio.html">Davide Di Ruscio</a>, <a href="../profile/RalfLämmel.html"><span class="info">Ralf Lämmel</span></a>, <a href="../profile/AlfonsoPierantonio.html">Alfonso Pierantonio</a>)</li>
<li><span class="info">(<a href="../sle2010/index.html">SLE 2010</a>)</span> <em>Coauthored <a href="../sle2010/paper11.html">A Unified Format for Language Documents</a></em> (<a href="../profile/VadimZaytsev.html">Vadim Zaytsev</a>, <a href="../profile/RalfLämmel.html"><span class="info">Ralf Lämmel</span></a>)</li>
<li><span class="info">(<a href="../sle2010/index.html">SLE 2010</a>)</span> <em>Coauthored <a href="../sle2010/paper19.html">Empirical Language Analysis in Software Linguistics</a></em> (<a href="../profile/JeanMarieFavre.html">Jean-Marie Favre</a>, <a href="../profile/DraganGašević.html">Dragan Gašević</a>, <a href="../profile/RalfLämmel.html"><span class="info">Ralf Lämmel</span></a>, <a href="../profile/EkaterinaPek.html">Ekaterina Pek</a>)</li>
<li><span class="info">(<a href="../sle2011/index.html">SLE 2011</a>)</span> <em>Coauthored <a href="../sle2011/paper16.html">Comparison of Context-Free Grammars Based on Parsing Generated Test Data</a></em> (<a href="../profile/BerndFischer.html">Bernd Fischer</a>, <a href="../profile/RalfLämmel.html"><span class="info">Ralf Lämmel</span></a>, <a href="../profile/VadimZaytsev.html">Vadim Zaytsev</a>)</li>
<li><span class="info">(<a href="../sle2013/index.html">SLE 2013</a>)</span> <em>Coauthored <a href="../sle2013/paper13.html">Method and Tool Support for Classifying Software Languages with Wikipedia</a></em> (<a href="../profile/RalfLämmel.html"><span class="info">Ralf Lämmel</span></a>, <a href="../profile/DominikMosen.html">Dominik Mosen</a>, <a href="../profile/AndreiVaranovich.html">Andrei Varanovich</a>)</li>
<li><span class="info">(<a href="../sle2014/index.html">SLE 2014</a>)</span> <em>Coauthored <a href="../sle2014/paper19.html">Test-Data Generation for Xtext (Tool Paper)</a></em> (<a href="../profile/JohannesHärtel.html">Johannes Härtel</a>, <a href="../profile/LukasHärtel.html">Lukas Härtel</a>, <a href="../profile/RalfLämmel.html"><span class="info">Ralf Lämmel</span></a>)</li>
