<li><span class="info">(<a href="../sle2016/index.html">SLE 2016</a>)</span> <em>Authored <a href="../sle2016/paper22.html">Coupled Software Transformations — Revisited</a></em> (<a href="../profile/RalfLämmel.html"><span class="info">Ralf Lämmel</span></a>)</li>
